	* dbus/upstart.h (DBUS_SERVICE_UPSTART, DBUS_ADDRESS_UPSTART):
	For debugging purposes, when -DDEBUG is given, change the values of
	these constants.  You'll need to modify your own D-Bus configuration
	of course.

